t: "wadhkuruu hyn yaqul 'ahl alshirk walnfaq wmrda alqlwb, wahum yarawn qlt almuslimin wakathrat edwhm: ghrr hwla' almuslimin dynuhm, fa'awradahum hadhih almward, walam yudrik hwla' almunafiqun 'anah min yatawakal ealaa allah wythq bwedh fa'iina allah ln ykhdhlh, fa'iina allah eaziz la yejzh shy', hakim fi tdbyrh wsneh"